      "e": "\"No matter A, B still holds.\" 不管 introduces a condition that makes no difference, and 都 stresses that the result never changes, as in 不管刮风下雨，我都得带它出去散步.",
      "x": "不管刮风下雨，我都得带它出去散步。 — No matter whether it's windy or raining, I have to take it out for a walk."
