    {
      "p": "甚至",
      "e": "甚至 means \"even\" and introduces the most extreme or surprising case in a list or statement, as in 我很累，甚至有点儿后悔养了它.",
      "x": "有一段时间我真的很累，甚至有点儿后悔养了它。 — For a while I was really exhausted; I even slightly regretted getting it."
